column16: Lance Berkman singles on a sharp line drive to catcher Jason Jaramillo, deflected by pitcher Chris Jakubauskas.    Michael Bourn to 2nd.
Pedro Feliz flies out to center fielder Andrew McCutchen.
Jeff Keppinger pops out softly to shortstop Ronny Cedeno.
Michael Bourn singles on a soft fly ball to left fielder Lastings Milledge.
